===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} {{term|πολύγλωττος||lang=grc|tr=poluglōttos|many-tongued, polyglot|sc=polytonic}}, from {{term|πολύς||tr=polus|lang=grc|many|sc=polytonic}} + {{term|γλῶττα||lang=grc|tr=glōtta|tongue, language|sc=polytonic}} (Attic variant of {{l|grc|γλῶσσα}}).

===Pronunciation===
